{"TopicId":217307,"ForumId":198,"TopicTitle":"Capture Mode When Using the NumPad Asterisk to Speed up Camera Movement also Changes Camera Rotation Speed To an Extreme Level","CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-21T23:59:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-21T23:59:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EKSP2 Version: \u003C/strong\u003E0.1.2.0.22258\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating System: \u003C/strong\u003EWindows 10\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECPU\u002BGPU\u002BRAM: \u003C/strong\u003Ei9 9900K\u002B3070ti\u002B32GB\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EMods Used:\u003C/strong\u003E None\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EObserved Behavior:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nUsing the Asterisk key to speed up camera mode also speeds up camera rotation.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EExpected Behavior:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nRotation speed should maintain whatever the default is for the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHow to Replicate:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLaunch a Craft\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nChange to Capture View\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nHold the NumPad * Key Down\u00A0 for a few seconds or more\u00A0and then\u00A0move the camera using the mouse.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-06-01T03:49:03Z\u0022 title=\u002206/01/2023 03:49  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJune 1, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Anth12\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bingmao","CreatedById":186983,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-03T05:25:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can confirm this. Also the camera rotation speed is carried over to (some) other views when switching to another view\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe speed carrying over is already reported in this bug:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022161238\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9521212834\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/217309-other-view-modes-are-inheriting-the-capture-modes-camera-speed-settings/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:194px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-06-03T05:32:31Z\u0022 title=\u002206/03/2023 05:32  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJune 3, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Bingmao\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}